# Law

Website for a law firm — public marketing site with practice areas, attorney profiles, and client intake.

## Status

Early stage. This repository currently contains project documentation only; application code has not been added yet.

## Planned Structure

| Page | Purpose |
| --- | --- |
| Home | Firm overview, primary call to action |
| Practice Areas | Services offered, one page per area |
| Attorneys | Bios, credentials, contact details |
| About | Firm history, values, locations |
| Contact | Intake form, office address, phone |

## Getting Started

Once a stack is chosen, this section should cover install, local dev server, and build commands.

```bash
git clone https://github.com/crtragency/Law.git
cd Law
```

## Contributing

Create a branch off `main`, commit your changes, and open a pull request.

